Name: Parry High
Text: If consumed, deal 1H at melee range immediately

Name: Parry Mid
Text: If consumed, deal 1M at melee range immediately

Name: Parry Low
Text: If consumed, deal 1L at melee range immediately

Name: Feint High
Text: Deals no damage. If blocked, reveal the top card of your deck, do any attacks on that card, then put that card on the bottom.

Text: Deals no damage. If blocked, reveal the top card of your deck, do any attacks on that card, then put that card on the bottom.

Text: Deals no damage. If blocked, reveal the top card of your deck, do any attacks on that card, then put that card on the bottom.
